com.example.app.repository

Interface Repository<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The Entity Type to be mapped by the repository.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PersonRepository

    public interface Repository<T>
    This interface abstracts the default CRUD methods to be implemented by Concrete classes. Implementing classes should pass as parameter the table Entity Type they abstract.
